<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Akses Ditolak</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: '#4F46E5',
                        secondary: '#10B981',
                        danger: '#EF4444',
                    },
                    animation: {
                        'bounce-slow': 'bounce 3s infinite',
                        'pulse-slow': 'pulse 3s infinite',
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3f4f6 0%, #e5e7eb 100%);
        }
        .card {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <svg class="relative block w-full h-20 text-blue-100" viewBox="0 0 1200 120" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path d="M0,0V6c0,21.6,291,111.46,741,110.26,445.39,3.6,459-88.3,459-110.26V0Z" class="shape-fill" fill="currentColor"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-lg w-full space-y-8 p-10 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl card border border-gray-100">
        <div class="text-center">
            <div class="mx-auto flex items-center justify-center h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-red-100 relative">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-ban text-red-500 text-6xl z-10"></i>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-red-100 rounded-full animate-ping opacity-20"></div>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="mt-6 text-9xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                403
            </h1>
            
            <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Akses Ditolak</h2>
            
            <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
                <p class="text-red-700 font-medium"><%= message %></p>
            </div>
            
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                Anda tidak memiliki izin yang diperlukan untuk mengakses halaman ini.
            </p>
            
            <div class="mt-8 bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Jika Anda merasa ini adalah kesalahan, silakan hubungi administrator sistem.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-purple-700 hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-primary focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-primary transition-all duration-300">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-house mr-2"></i> Kembali ke Dashboard
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full overflow-hidden pointer-events-none rotate-180">
        <svg class="relative block w-full h-20 text-blue-100" viewBox="0 0 1200 120" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path d="M0,0V6c0,21.6,291,111.46,741,110.26,445.39,3.6,459-88.3,459-110.26V0Z" class="shape-fill" fill="currentColor"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>
</body>
</html>